1.Go to the kitty exapmle config file in root directory and copy it to the i3/.config directory

$cp /kitty/kitty.conf /.config/i3/kitty

2.Change the setting of the opacity
opacity 0.85

3.Download xcompmgr (composite manager)
$sudo pacman -S xcompmgr

4.Add to i3 config file
$exec xcompmgr -c -f -n
